OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FLargely sunny and very warm,
OL,6,Flocally hot, once any early morning
OL,7,Fcloud burns back to the coast. Cooler
OL,8,Falong the coast with cloud lingering
OL,9,Fthere, this could move inland from
OL,10,Fearly evening as a northeasterly
OL,11,Fbreeze develops.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FLow cloud will spread quickly
OL,14,Fsouthwest across the region overnight,
OL,15,Fdriven by a northeasterly breeze.
OL,16,FTemperatures remain mild but cooler
OL,17,Falong the coast.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
