OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CSunday:FCloudy periods to start
OL,6,FSunday, skies will clear giving a
OL,7,Fbright and sunny afternoon.
OL,8,FTemperatures inland stay very warm but
OL,9,Fcooler along the coast in the
OL,10,Fnortheasterly breeze.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:FDry
OL,13,Fand largely sunny conditions on Monday
OL,14,Fwith coastal cloud. Some patchy cloud
OL,15,FTuesday morning, brightening up later.
OL,16,FFoggy and cloudy start to Wednesday
OL,17,Fwith afternoon sunshine. Temperatures
OL,18,Faround average.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
